4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience who aspire to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, with three live online classes each week. Participants will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with advanced topics such as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The class size is limited to 16 students to ensure personalized attention. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop